routeFacts.name: Cane Creek
routeFacts.description: Cane Creek is a route for Train Sim World 2. It features the 40.8 mile (56.3 km) route from Thompson to Potash owned by Union Pacific. This is the first add-on in Train Sim World made by Skyhook Games.
routeInfo: This Route follows the Cane Creek branchline from Brendel, Utah to Potash, Utah a few miles from Moab, as well as a five mile portion of the Union Pacific Green River Subdivision mainline between Brendel and Thompson. The Cane Creek line is used by a Friday Potash local and a Uranium Tailings Train running as needed these are at least in real life.
